AsyncMode Example

VB Example:

With m_spel

    .AsyncMode = True

    .Jump("pick")

    .Delay(500)

    .On(1)

    WaitCommandComplete()

End With

C# Example:

m_spel.AsyncMode = true;

m_spel.Jump("pick");

m_spel.Delay(500);

m_spel.On(1);

m_spel.WaitCommandComplete();

